I guess the question I wonder is, why was that nut ever removed in the
first place?   I know that doesn't help now...I guess I would take various
nuts from other things and try one until you find one that fits, then take
it to the shop to get another one.,  now this is the one on the side of
the tranny right??   the other two are a clevis pin and a ball and socket.

> thread it is.  Also, any good reference sites for the T2-Automatic would be
