Bus Depot may have one of the trouble shooting manuals left, Ron found
some NOS manuals and he had a tranny one for the 010 auto tranny which is
what your bus "should" have in it.

the "orange" VW service manual has a little more on the trannies than the
"green" Bentley manuals but they are much harder to find...

send me a private e-mail and maybe I can help you with the tranny pages.
